snippet.title: The Sims Mobile (iOS/Android) Soft Launch Trailer | Official Mobile Game
snippet.description: Coming Soon, The Sims Mobile (iOS/Android) is an Official Mobile Game by Maxis Studios and Electronic Arts. Shape your Sims’ legacy as you create their unique personalities, homes, and relationships. Visit www.thesims.com/mobile  for more information and to subscribe to updates.
